<br>
<h2> Become a "Self Pay" Provider! </h2>
<br>

<%= form_tag "/providers", method: :post do %>

  <form class="form_container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-3 mb-3">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="zipcode" placeholder="Zip Code" required>
      </div>
      <p> Enter your <strong> zipcode </strong> and your most commonly billed <strong> CPT codes </strong> to see Self Pay's Rates. </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <%index = 1 %>
      <% 8.times do %>
        <div class="col-sm-3 mb-3">
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="procedure_code<%=index%>" placeholder="CPT Code">
          <% index += 1 %>
        </div>
      <%end%>
    </div>

    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Submit form</button>

  </form>
<% end %>

<br> 
<p> What does it mean to be a self pay provider? </p> 
<ul class= "provider_summary">
  <li> Potential Self Pay patients will see you listed as a participating provider </li>
  <li> You agree to bill Self Pay patients at the Self Pay rate </li>
  <li> Self Pay Rates are Medicare's Non-Facility Rates +15% </li>
  <li> Self Pay patients can mention this site to receive the discount </li>
  <li> Come and go as a you wish - signing up and canceling is done with the click of a button </li>
</ul>

 

  







